<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē bhūtanētrāmṛtaruciśaśibhirvvarttamānē <unclear>ku</unclear>ḷīraṁ yātē pyallaṁḍavāsī nijaguṇaniratō rekka
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nākhyō dinēṁdrē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādāddīpaṁ śubhārtthaṁ sakalamunisuraissēvyamānāya tasmai śrīmatsiṁhādridhāmnē naraharivapu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṣē yāvadācaṁdratāraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1125 gunēṇṭi karkkāṭakasaṁkrāṁttinimittyamugā śrīmatsiṁhagiri
<lb n="4"/>śrīnarasiṁhadēvaraku Allaṁḍaśāsanikuṁḍaina rēkamanāyakuṁḍu peṭṭina Akhaṁḍadīpa mokkaṇṭiki nitya narasiṁha
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mānika mānaṁḍu nēti lekka nācaṁdrārkkamuṁ jallaṁgga<supplied reason="omitted">la</supplied>yadigā Ī dēvara śrībhaṁḍāramuna noḍkina surabhigadya lēḍu Ī
<lb n="6"/>māḍalu gajamajice<unclear>ṛvu</unclear>naṁ beṭṭi groppiṁcchuṭaṁ jēsi Ī ceṟvukṛṁda vuṭṭaṁḍu<unclear>nē</unclear>ṁdumu bhūmi phalabhōgamunaṁdu callu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭaku śrāvaṇasahitamugā peṭṭiri <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasuṁdhdharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭhi<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>varṣa sahasrāṇi viṣṭhāyā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁ jāyatē kṛmiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ī dharmmuvu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī yūri sōviraḍi baṁdaṁ beṭṭi groppiṁcchiri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

